PREREQUISITES

1. Postfix installed.
1. Spamasssin installed.
1. basic_filter installed.

INSTALL

In the conf/ directory you will find the basic Postfix configuration files for a unxsMail controlled system.

To install follow the following steps:

1. Shutdown Postfix (if running)
2. Copy the files in the conf/ dir to /etc/postfix
3. Open /etc/postfix/main.cf with your favourite text editor
4. Edit the value of myhostname and inet_interfaces variables
3. Start Postfix

